data.description: Located in the serene villa community of Amber Lake is this spacious home with a split bedroom floor plan. Through the covered front porch and into the entryway you will find a large great room with 10 foot ceilings, gas fireplace, and wall of windows that looks out onto the covered back porch with ceiling fan and patio extension. The primary suite has a tray ceiling and spacious bathroom with dual closets, walk-in shower, and double vanity. Some of the updates to the home include a refreshed 2nd bath with modern details, lots of new paint throughout, new exterior lighting, many new interior lights, new kitchen sink with accessories, front and bathroom windows recently replaced, interior door hardware, and some new flooring. This home even has a central vac system. HVAC was just serviced and cleaning of ductwork and carpets has just been completed. Ring doorbell, washer, dryer and all kitchen appliances included but not warranted.
